### Task 9: Behavioral Engine — 9 Detectors + Composite ✅
- `portfolio_doctor/core/behavioral_engine.py` — 9 standalone detectors + composite
- `detect_panic_selling()` — sells when Nifty >10% below 52-week high, cost = recovery opportunity
- `detect_fomo_buying()` — buys when Nifty near ATH (<2% from peak) or stock >20% above 200 DMA
- `detect_disposition_effect()` — FIFO lot matching, compares winner vs loser holding periods
- `detect_overtrading()` — round-trip detection (buy+sell same stock within 30 days)
- `detect_concentration_risk()` — single-stock weight thresholds (>20/30/40%)
- `detect_herd_behavior()` — buys after >30% rally in prior month
- `detect_anchoring_bias()` — sells within ±2% of avg buy price (breakeven anchoring)
- `detect_sip_discipline()` — crash-period detection + SIP span checking
- `detect_regular_plan_waste()` — "Regular" in scheme_name detection + TER drag estimate
- `compute_behavioral_composite()` — weighted average with spec weights, top-3 issues by cost
- Shared helpers: `_nearest_value()`, `_peak_in_window()`, `_find_crash_dates()`, `_score_to_severity()`
- `tests/portfolio_doctor/core/test_behavioral_engine.py` — 31 tests (3 panic, 3 FOMO, 3 disposition, 3 overtrading, 3 concentration, 3 herd, 3 anchoring, 3 SIP, 3 regular plan, 4 composite)

